## ⚠️ CRITICAL RULES

1. **DO NOT share your screen** with other teams. You have information they don't — that's the point.
2. **Verbal communication is mandatory** between you and your partner. You MUST describe what you see on your screen.
3. **If your screen says "ACCESS DENIED"**, it means only your partner can do that action. Tell them what you need.
4. **If you get caught by a Sec-Bot**, your character resets to the start of the map. Keep your Intel Officer on overwatch duty!
5. **Do not refresh the page** mid-round — you may lose your progress.
6. **Only one player navigates the map at a time** — the Field Agent controls movement while the Intel Officer watches from above.

